parameters: It's just an ordinary well that can be found anywhere.

...There is a sad story about this well. Long ago...
children were playing hide and seek. One girl in particular
didn't want to be found until the very end.

The girl who tried various hiding places ended up at this
well. She was strictly disciplined by the adults because it
was very dangerous. The village children were forbidden from
approaching the well under any circumstances.

And as expected... tragedy struck. While descending to the
lower level, the rope snapped. The girl ended up falling to
the bottom of the well.

The bottom of the well was freezing cold, mercilessly
stealing away the girl's body heat. Her desperate cries for
help did not reach anyone.

Eventually, she lost the strength to cry out and stopped
feeling the cold. Fading in and out of consciousness, she
had already resigned herself to death, despite being so
young. And surprisingly, that girl...

\SE[0]Oh my! If Lunaroa hadn't saved me back then, I might
have really died...!
\SM[nod]\SE[29]I got scolded by my father a lot... Haha...

You're a boring pig who doesn't get along with people. The
fun pigs are at the ranch on the left!

Laura's house! ... It's a sign that was built when I was a
child. Now I feel embarrassed about it and want to take it
down. But my father looks really lonely.

Lunaroa's house! ... This sign was made by the two of us
when we were children. If it were to disappear, it would be
very lonely, so I can understand my father's feelings a
little.

The untended pond can become a breeding ground for pests!
Let's gather donations and proceed with filling it up
together! For more details, please contact Debo in the
warehouse.
\SE[2] I don't really mind either way.
『Ito』is full of danger! Let's use it together with adults!

Oh, Laura-chan! Listen to this! My old man keeps bugging me
to get married soon! Can you believe how impatient he is?

\SE[15]Isn't it great to get married! If it's Bolt-san, he
seems like he would make a wonderful dad.

Eh, eh hehe... Is that so? My old man was saying something
like Wouldn't it be nice if it was someone like Laura-chan?
Even if he says something like that, it's kind of troubling,
isn't it...?

Y-Yeah, that's right! S-Something like that would never
happen, right?! It's really troublesome with my parents too!
Haha...

\SE[100]Hmm... I feel like I have to witness the battle
between these two...

It's Laura-san's father... Alright... First, I need to
establish a solid foundation with her parents... I'll make
sure to attack from all sides...

Ugh... I can't move my legs...! Now is the time to gather my
strength...! Dammit... Why...? Dammit... Dammit...!

Oh, it's Laura-chan! You're energetic as always today! Your
father is working diligently, so you can rest assured!

\SE[22]Ahaha. \SE[0]My father may be pathetic, but please
take care of me \SM[nod]and treat me well.

There was also something like this... I think both of us
have probably forgotten though.

The reason I came here... was to ensure that exceptional
talent doesn't go unnoticed in the frontier... In other
words, it was for the purpose of inspecting and scouting
Lunaroa-san.

To assess her talent... and her 'aptitude'... Needless to
say, it was exceptionally outstanding, to the point where it
was impossible to hide.

Young Laura said, I didn't intend to 'kidnap' Lunaroa-san.
Of course, I never had any such intention.

As a result, it may have turned out that way. She will be
invited to the magic academy as a scholarship student. ... I
ended up taking away her lover from her.

I feel like I'm causing more unhappiness. I had confidence
in my strategy... but... it's not going well. I'm troubled.
And then, a little while... time has passed.
